STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Jamaal GEORGE, a/k/a James George, Speedy, Defendant-Petitioner. C-916 September Term 2017
080591 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004810-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
